snippet.title: LOVE - A Puzzle Box Filled with Stories - Debut Trailer (Updated)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam -  https://store.steampowered.com/app/12...
Coming 2020 - http://thatlovegame.com

Every life has a story. Every story has regret. But what if you could change the past? LOVE is a puzzle game about finding the things we’ve lost in ourselves and the people who help us find them.

LOVE - A Puzzle Box Filled with Stories was made possible with the support of Ontario Creates. To learn more, visit http://www.ontariocreates.ca
